==English==

===Etymology===
''[[post-]]'' + ''[[script]]''

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#{{countable}} An [[addendum]] to a [[letter]], added after the author's [[signature]].

====Usage note====
In a letter, to indicate the beginning of a postscript one often uses the abbreviation ''[[PS]]'' followed by a colon.

